{% apply spaceless %}
{% apply inline_css %}
    <style>
        #message {
            background-color: rgb(175, 200, 185);
            padding: 20px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        h2 { text-align: center; }
        a { color: blue; }
    </style>
    <div id="message">
        <h2>You've been invited to FapBot! ðŸ¥³</h2>
        <hr/>
        <p>
            <strong>Hi {{ user.username }},</strong>
            We'd like to welcome you to the moderation team!<br/>
            It can be quite a lot to keep track of which user was muted or warned on what days and what for,
            to make this part of our job easier, we have FapBot. <br/>
            <br/>
            FapBot can be used to mute and warn users, it'll automatically unmute users, inform you when a troublesome
            user has gotten a lot of warnings, and it allows you to look of the user history.<br/>
            <br/>
            <strong>Accessing FapBot</strong><br/>
            Website: <a href="https://fapbot.tech/{{ path('user_login') }}">https://fapbot.tech/{{ path('user_login') }}</a><br/>
            Username: {{ user.username }}<br/>
            <br/>
            You can create your first password by clicking on this link: <a href="https://fapbot.tech/{{ path('create_password', { 'id': user.id, 'secret': secret }) }}">Create password</a><br/>
            <br/>
            <strong>Getting started</strong><br/>
            Once you've logged in you'll have access to the guide where you can find all the ins and outs of using
            FapBot. When you've read through that try muting and warning yourself, you can always unmute early.<br/>
        </p>
    </div>
{% endapply %}
{% endapply %}